{"tid":1533702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"各位善長人翁，宣明會咁多醜聞，啲捐款又送中，你仲捐得落手？","createTime":"2019-09-02T19:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:01:07.000Z","uid":38376,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6e45157a7755313cf2e8914cb5b0602399f81358","tid":1533702,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:34:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位善長人翁，宣明會高層每年支取6百萬年薪，你哋嘅善款真係比佢哋每年搭飛機周圍去，食好西<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWYg8SV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWYg8SV.jpg&h=d0ea8198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且，中國接受嘅善款有超過6成係黎自香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ns9TrKJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fns9TrKJ.jpg&h=4207ca52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲爆咁多醜聞<br />\n[size=4]<span style=\"color: blue;\">宣明會承認貪污，及要求女災民以性服務換糧食援助<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180220/20309906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F20309906&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=493f7c4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F20309906&h=b581ec46\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180220/20309906</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180218/mobile/bknint-20180218150855747-0218_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180218%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180218150855747-0218_17011_001.html&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=8c201d4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180218/mobile/bknint-20180218150855747-0218_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/wo/647271/日報-國際-宣明會再爆醜聞-職員要求災民以性換糧\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fwo%2F647271%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%AE%A3%E6%98%8E%E6%9C%83%E5%86%8D%E7%88%86%E9%86%9C%E8%81%9E-%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%81%BD%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%A5%E6%80%A7%E6%8F%9B%E7%B3%A7&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=bf5b470f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fwo%2F647271%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%AE%A3%E6%98%8E%E6%9C%83%E5%86%8D%E7%88%86%E9%86%9C%E8%81%9E-%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%81%BD%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%A5%E6%80%A7%E6%8F%9B%E7%B3%A7&h=5d1acd8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/wo/647271/日報-國際-宣明會再爆醜聞-職員要求災民以性換糧</a></span>[/size=3]<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">我想講，當你d捐款係咁比高層出糧，係咁送比中國，香港仲有好多自己人需要我地幫咖，介紹比大家丫：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蘋果日報慈善基金</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3retbOv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3retbOv.png&h=6530ae83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果日報慈善基金係香港認可嘅慈善機構，捐款<strong><ins>可以報稅</ins></strong>之餘，最重要係善款唔會亂用<br />\n<br />\n你唔會見到高層支薪幾百萬，唔會見到要求受助人用性/做義工黎交換援助，唔會見到基金喺TVB/學校/單張不斷大賣廣告<br />\n<br />\n求吓你地，我地每日150個已經幫左中國好多喇，而家就cut左宣明會，轉去蘋果慈善基金，幫吓自己人啦。<br />\n<br />\n好人健康長久！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"1c2b069a54e9eb2f6256f856e8bba6f42a4980a7","tid":1533702,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:37:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蘋果慈善基金<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk-charity.nextmedia.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk-charity.nextmedia.com%2F&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=95de37ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk-charity.nextmedia.com%2F&h=42b25ba1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk-charity.nextmedia.com/</a></span>"},{"pid":"aa8a7772ef8fff08be0d3e8986b10f7b70708ee6","tid":1533702,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:38:43.000Z","msg":"前兩日見到有手足拆狗鐘啲站，其實有個啟示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533701</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9f1168682b124930a60343e7dab165ece378d55c","tid":1533702,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:40:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蘋果日報慈善基金捐款網頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk-charity.nextmedia.com/site/index.php?fuseaction=site.donationArea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk-charity.nextmedia.com%2Fsite%2Findex.php%3Ffuseaction%3Dsite.donationArea&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=55ce9322\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk-charity.nextmedia.com%2Fsite%2Findex.php%3Ffuseaction%3Dsite.donationArea&h=cc13f573\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk-charity.nextmedia.com/site/index.php?fuseaction=site.donationArea</a></span>"},{"pid":"ad7c909d526f890d5e296e075b59379ff0d20d4f","tid":1533702,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:42:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18d52e649e769ac42032667fd15b78e2542b8369","tid":1533702,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e871705b03a836c870f606097e53c987273316a7","tid":1533702,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:21:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d2307d711a1fa0768f838e3c50277f741432517","tid":1533702,"uid":277044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:25:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98f84f365d84178f620d219d4e5420da5d514576","tid":1533702,"uid":277044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:25:22.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"7f0c1f580ee1761af42a4ed918b83f88f2bb30ce","tid":1533702,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:16:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f9fae692cfda1c21552321dbd047a69d6c56708","tid":1533702,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54afa55a19499ae2ab9f38ce99ab2820da704c43","tid":1533702,"uid":197958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"落地獄"},{"pid":"939a046ed412580370575eae5df85cf9a70dcfd5","tid":1533702,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:06.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"a0271cd46c16de157b648610840beb79cc1ca1f5","tid":1533702,"uid":260371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:38:40.000Z","msg":"如果商台再同宣明會合作搞饑饉30就連商台都杯埋！"},{"pid":"b6b8d245d6aace10f2a63f60e206d51fdd763166","tid":1533702,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d308da2ca1fd12992790d84c011eed39c4be57","tid":1533702,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2bebca37b1cce2d62ab4a48592b2af83f57b23","tid":1533702,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c5ca2f04fe0fdf888bd94f5120ed2f8db218b1","tid":1533702,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:26:32.000Z","msg":"宣暗會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfc98689b9bf2ad5613523465ae211b75b22302","tid":1533702,"uid":74043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:33:06.000Z","msg":"咪撚再捐比呢啲賤種機構"},{"pid":"fc7ecca468892d20bcbc5bd86b26400fbbada02f","tid":1533702,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:38:48.000Z","msg":"一蚊唔捐NGO"},{"pid":"f5db4d3cdcd357a925df89149af0fa3c6d1d9346","tid":1533702,"uid":74913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:39:26.000Z","msg":"善長&quot;仁&quot;翁"},{"pid":"04a4f9955637cedb0faf79b93f3f17a15ed35da9","tid":1533702,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5db4d3cdcd357a925df89149af0fa3c6d1d9346","tid":1533702,"uid":74913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:39:26.000Z","msg":"善長&quot;仁&quot;翁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}